5 August 2008The Minister of Public Enterprise Alec Erwin and the Director-General of the Department of Justice and Constitutional Development, Menzi Simelane, will on Wednesday, 6 August 2008, brief the media on the Strategic Defence Procurement (Arms Deal).The details of the briefing are as follows:Venue: Union Buildings; Room 153 Date: 6 August 2008 (Tomorrow) Time: 16:00NB: There will be a video link with Cape Town; Imbizo Media Centre.Enquiries Harold Maloka (Pretoria) Cell: 082 847 9799Collin Cruywagen (Cape Town) Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)